import { Link } from "react-router-dom"
import './Nav.css'


function Nav() {
    return(
        <>
            <nav class="nav nav-pills nav-fill">
               <Link to="/" class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Home</Link>
               <Link to="/Cliente" class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Cliente</Link>
               <Link to="/Servico" class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Serviços</Link>
            </nav>  
        </>
    )
}

export default Nav
